   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Summary & Recommendations\n",
    "\n",
    "✅ You now have:\n",
    "- Streaming ingestion from Kafka\n",
    "- Raw storage (bronze)\n",
    "- Product-level aggregations\n",
    "- DynamoDB sink (via pandas workaround)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Production improvements**:\n",
    "- Use Databricks Jobs + Delta Live Tables (DLT) for orchestration\n",
    "- Write bronze to S3 via Unity Catalog external location (paid tier)\n",
    "- Use DynamoDB Sink connector or foreachBatch for true streaming write\n",
    "- Add watermarking + windowing for aggregations\n",
    "- Monitor with Spark UI / Ganglia\n",
    "\n",
    "Happy streaming! 🚀"
   ]
  }
 ],
